736
01:04:36,803 --> 01:04:39,465
We have his credit cards,
his cell phone.

737
01:04:39,572 --> 01:04:42,735
<i>He has no other place to hide.</i>

738
01:04:54,487 --> 01:04:57,320
- Can I help you?
- Oh, yes, ma'am.

739
01:04:57,423 --> 01:05:01,826
My name is Lawson Smith.
I'm looking for a Walter Xavier.

740
01:05:01,928 --> 01:05:06,888
Oh, lovely boy,
but he been gone a long time.

741
01:05:07,000 --> 01:05:11,630
- Well, this is the address
we have on his sweepstakes form.
